Stat History ============ Starting January 1st 2026, the Feign Renderer will begin keeping track of the average render times, and various errors for each of its unit tests on a daily basis. These metrics will be reported to keep track of the Feign Renderer's performance as new features are continuously added. All unit tests are ran on a single thread using the same computer to maintain consistency.
